# The ESPN Fantasy API is typically accessed from two endpoints:
New API as of May 2024: https://lm-api-reads.fantasy.espn.com/apis/v3/games/ffl/seasons/2023/segments/0/leagues/REDACTED_LEAGUE_ID
For seasons >= 2018: https://fantasy.espn.com/apis/v3/games/ffl/seasons/2023/segments/0/leagues/REDACTED_LEAGUE_ID
For seasons <= 2017: https://fantasy.espn.com/apis/v3/games/ffl/leagueHistory/{league_id}?seasonId={season}

